61,"uid":38794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"1. 其實，即使一國一制，都不會衝公你身家。除非你要著草，因此大型銀行放錢已足夠。<br />\n2. 換美元是防港元脫勾。<br />\n3. 輸有限（因為有聯匯）。<br />\n4. 防港元資產大跌，換美元資產（如美股美債）。<br />\n5. 香港03 年樓市暴跌，銀行也不會死，當然業主另計。"},{"pid":"a47857ed3da54961fb6ef224fe5bace4e0d3c36d","tid":1460261,"uid":111811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31fb2a8940b37f03caa8b63f26b6fa9947777a64","tid":1460261,"uid":53368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:41:15.000Z","msg":"今日渣打網上換 7.874"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:00:49.000Z","msg":"早兩個月試過喺7.83換到美元<br />\n而家升到7.86, 7.87"},{"pid":"9e3addd825555a88950a4614621949cfb67b8e8f","tid":1460261,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:01:19.000Z","msg":"無美金backup既港紙係無價值<br />\n無港紙backup既人仔同冥通無分別"},{"pid":"0517510d10b98fdf596e0d013a8a9a1868332934","tid":1460261,"uid":270563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5abf64c7238204f3c147e960bc41575706e42a0d","tid":1460261,"uid":218648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"其實個聯系匯率係靠個外匯儲備去維持，個問題係大家信唔信香港個4500億外匯儲備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外資走，個外匯儲備會跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6597280f0760bb8b465a3c7d77528c18800135","tid":1460261,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae67f929ad2b70d9e42d90605252eb9cb23f6c35","tid":1460261,"uid":179679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"因為美金係全球最有認受性嘅貨幣<br />\n中國 印度 仲有好多大國都係用美金做交易貨幣<br />\n換句說話講 姐係全球都對美金最有信心<br />\n<br />\n香港仲同美金掛緊勾<br />\n但萬一香港出咩事 港幣被恐慌性拋售 金管局頂唔住7.85 你手上美金相對住港幣就會升到仆街<br />\n姐係你有賺"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-0